Ice used her telekinetic powers to move rubble away. Her and Lunarpine had
to act fast. The heat from the bombs had weakened the structure of the cave.
melted ice dripped down on the two rescuers as they battled thier way
through. Finally Lunarpine caught Grizzltrons scent. He dug through until he
found the other bot in stasis lock. Ice helped lift the injured bot onto the
shoulders of the half wolf.

They forced thier way out just on time to see the top of the hillside
collapse into the caves below.

&quot;Now what should we do with him?&quot; Lunarpine asked torn between saving and
finishing off the bot.

Ice smiled at the compasion Lunarpine seemed to be showing  even though she
could sense his quarel with himself. &quot;Veratis said to come get him, I think
we should take him back for observation.&quot;

Lunarpine checked the bots condition once more wondering if it was safe to
move him. realizing that there was no other logical choice he summoned the
drones, strapped one to Grizzltron and sent the other one over to Ice. Ice
refused the chivalrous offer knowing that Lunarpine needed it more than she
did. The mutant transformed to her owl form and started flying back towards
Norway.

Lunarpine quickly caught up scooping her out of the air in his strong,
powerfull arms. He had remained in half wolf mode for the added benefit of
the extra strength. As they flew Ice transformed to her odd robot mode and
kissed the half wolf on the cheek. Grizzletrons drone followed closely set
on autopilot it made it&#39;s way toward home.


